<template>
  <v-carousel interval="4500" style="width: 95%!important" >
    <v-carousel-item
      v-for="(item,i) in items"
      :key="i"
      :src="item.src"
    ></v-carousel-item>
  </v-carousel>

</template>

<script>
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        items: [
          {
            src: require('@/assets/salavelacionnumeros.png')
          },
          {
            src: require('@/assets/colmena3.png')
          },
          {
            src: require('@/assets/DJI_0031.png')
          },
          {
            src: require('@/assets/asomavicontexto.png')
          },
          {
            src: require('@/assets/z.jpg')
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
</script>
